"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-01-steven-van-de-veldes-partner-pleads-olympic-crowds-boos-rapist-21339941\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Steven van de Velde's partner says he was 'disappointed' with the crowd reaction after the convicted rapist was relentlessly booed again at theOlympic GamesinParis.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 19, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999985169826769, \"rank\": 1.4830194261363187e-06, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde was sentenced to four years in prison in 2016after pleading guilty to raping a 12-year-old British girl when he was 19.\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 270, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8260177620459453, \"rank\": 0.17102372984230885, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He resumed his volleyball career after serving 12 months of a four-year sentence and was named in the Netherlands' Olympic squad in June.\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8800128815534648, \"rank\": 0.13611606750030858, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  The 29-year-old wasbooed during his first appearance at the beach volleyball event on Sundayand was given an even more hostile reception as the Dutch took on Chile on Wednesday afternoon.\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.7832211001829793, \"rank\": 0.2701837793570624, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 670, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9904783934533793, \"rank\": 0.007084948315671012, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde was booed every time he served at the Eiffel Tower Stadium with his volleyball partner Matthew Immers again defending his teammate.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not want to say much about it.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What was in the past is in the past,' he told reporters.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I can not change his past.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am here to play with him.\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 996, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to have good results here.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are a lot of people who support us.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We do it for them.\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'He has a lot of pressure on his shoulders.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am OK with that.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mentally we are strong, I am strong, we will get through this together.'\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the increased booing van de Velde received, Immers added: 'It is what it is.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999985169826769, \"rank\": 1.4830194261363187e-06, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was disappointed with the fans.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We talked on the field and asked ourselves: what do we need from each other?\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was worse than in the first game.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We need each other on the field, the hugs, the cheering.'\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van de Velde's inclusion in the Dutch squad has been persistently defendedby teammates and the team's selectors and decision-makers.\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.7832211001829793, \"rank\": 0.2701837793570624, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Steven has been active in international sports and the beach volleyball world for a long time,' Van den Hoogenband, who won swimming gold medals at the 2000 and 2004 Olympics, told Dutch outlet NOS a